<thetext>Description of problem: It would be nice if one could list all metrics from a subtree per instance, as in &quot;tell me everything what is known about cpu2&quot; or &quot;show me all the metrics related to PID 1&quot;. So ideally for example
&quot;pmval -i cpu2 hinv&quot; or &quot;pmdumptext -i -l &apos;proc.psinfo[1]&apos;&quot; would work.</thetext>
</long_desc>
