<thetext>Since PCP 3.11.10 this is possible with something like: $ pmrep -v -i cpu2 hinv $ pmrep -v -i &quot;&apos;000001 /usr/lib/systemd/systemd&apos;&quot; proc.psinfo $ pmrep -v -I -i &apos;cpu.*&apos; &quot;&quot; Thanks.</thetext>
